  "body": "<center><img alt=\"GIaB\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/OPyn7IN9/images/2f688afbe72259f49751cce0261b743073e6250a.png\"></center>\n\n## Description\nThis pack replaces GUI icons in the style of cells. Any matches with flags are random. The set does not carry a semantic load.\n\n## Installing\nThe resource pack must be placed in the resourcepacks folder in the .minecraft directory\n\nDefault: \n* Windows: **C:\\\\Users\\\\%USERNAME%\\\\AppData\\\\Roaming\\\\.minecraft\\\\resourcepacks\\\\**\n* Linux: **~/.minecraft/resourcepacks**\n\nNext, in Minecraft, go to **[Settings]** -> **[Resource Packs]** -> Select the desired pack -> **[Done]**\n\n## Requirements\n* Minecraft version higher than **1.8**\n\n## Feedback\nYou can contact us via [email](mailto:mystyhaddock355@ya.ru) or [Discord](https://discord.com/users/817075264567115806).\n\n## Finance/referal support\n[![🚀 Host with aéza – Fast, Secure & Affordable](https://img.shields.io/badge/aéza%20vps%20hosting-%E2%82%AC4.94%2Fmo%2B-purple?style=for-the-badge&logo=linux)](https://aeza.net/?ref=724303)\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bZTgH6Lk/images/e6ee8090f49140f4bb1ba886d26c795ced9a79ad.png\" width=160 heght=48></img>\n```\nTGjiLho2eUMRAMPf6PUZs16EF2cvphnv8d\n```\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bZTgH6Lk/images/1fa354a88c1846b75d48d6a8988e0731a5271251.png\" width=160 heght=48></img>\n```\n1dvL4mQf7cMmXhLc3A2tiyymVDF19TJnV\n```\n\n## My (our) projects\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/totems_o_players\" title=\"Totems'o'players\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/lhXx6Sw8/524d5de9d0f8b6b8cd4f5731f1a376487e7f99ff.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/alt-swords-classic\" title=\"Alt-Swords Classic\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/OYHTUzqk/3ff31c40daf54682cccbc41c26ab7de27c1eefd1.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/simple-banhammer\" title=\"Sim